http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/AP-a-safe-state-for-investments-says-Chief-Whip/article13997394.ece

Chief Whip Kalva Srinivasulu on Wednesday opined that Andhra Pradesh was a safe and secured place for the investors to invest their money.Talking to media persons after offering prayers at the hill temple of Lord Venkateswara, Mr. Srinivasulu said that investors from several countries had come forward and inked pacts worth several lakhs of crores of rupees with the state government.This defines the success of the three-day CII Partnership Summit that concluded recently at Visakhapatnam. But for the determination and strong leadership qualities of Chief Minister N. Chandrababu Naidu the investors would not have come forward to invest in the State he said.